    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Expert Hunter (5e)</p><p>5e. Also at 21st level, your skill in hunting your favored enemy has translated into almost all quarry you hunt. When you finish a long rest, choose 3 additional favored enemy options. You can change these options after you finish a long rest. You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls against your favored enemies.</p></div>",
